# Create a new template

1) Export the oc new-app output in yaml format using the GitHub repo https://github.com/mmul-it/docker with
   the context dir ncat-msg-http-port and the name mmul in a new yaml file

2) Edit the file replacing everything necessary to makes it a Template with three parameters: NAME, REPLICAS
   and PORT

3) Add the parameters section with default values and descriptions for each parameter

4) Create the template and check if parameters are defined correctly

5) Try deploying a new app from this template. Check if everyting is ok and follow the BuildConfig

6) Try exposing the new app and check from a browser if works
